caption%3EThe%20charger%20has%20a%20built-in%20USB-C%20cable%2C%20so%20you%20never%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20misplacing%20the%20cord.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20are%20many%20reasons%20I%20think%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126413087sjg-20%26h%3Da8ea24c9e265a6f2033070a1bbd6be61c327033252cd4916f150d1b887614b4b%26postID%3D69fb944131845c865e3bde24%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fanker-nano-power-bank-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FAnker-Power-Built-Retractable-USB-C%252Fdp%252FB0DGKWTQQC%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnker%20Nano%20Power%20Bank%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20great%20portable%20battery%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20features%20stand%20out%20in%20particular%3A%20its%20%3Cstrong%3Ehigh%20capacity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20(without%20being%20bulky)%20and%20its%20%3Cstrong%3Ebuilt-in%20charging%20cable%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20keep%20your%20phone%20powered%20throughout%20a%20trip%2C%20your%20portable%20battery%20needs%20to%20have%20enough%20juice%20to%20recharge%20it.%20The%20Anker%20Nano%20Power%20Bank%20has%20a%2010%2C000%20mAh%20capacity%2C%20and%20I've%20found%20it%20perfect%20for%20a%20long%20day%20away%20from%20outlets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cstrong%3E10K%20capacity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20offers%20an%20ideal%20balance%20between%20physical%20size%20and%20charging%20power.%20For%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fiphone-17-pro-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EiPhone%2017%20Pro%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20can%20get%20about%20two%20extra%20charges%20from%20the%20Nano.%20In%20practice%2C%20while%20traveling%2C%20I%20use%20the%20Nano%20to%20top%20up%20my%20phone%20multiple%20times%20throughout%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20on%20a%20recent%20cross-country%20trip%2C%20I%20used%20the%20Nano%20Power%20Bank%20at%20the%20airport%20gate.%20(I%20seem%20to%20always%20find%20the%20seat%20with%20a%20non-working%20outlet.)%20While%20I%20waited%20and%20downloaded%20music%2C%20the%20Nano%20boosted%20my%20phone's%20battery%20by%2015%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20other%20times%2C%20I'll%20give%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-the-newest-ipad%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EiPad%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fapple-macbook-neo-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMacBook%20Neo%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20bump%20%E2%80%94%20enough%20to%20finish%20the%20night%20or%20make%20it%20to%20another%20wall%20outlet.%20And%20while%20on%20a%20plane%2C%20I%20can%20easily%20plug%20the%20Nano%20into%20my%20laptop's%20side%20port%20without%20fiddling%20with%20the%20outlet%20under%20my%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Nano%20Power%20Bank's%20%3Cstrong%3Ebuilt-in%202.3-foot%20USB-C%20cable%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20the%20other%20key%20feature%20I%20love.%20It's%20freeing%20not%20having%20to%20pull%20out%20the%20power%20bank%20%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20wire%20from%20my%20bag%20and%20then%20keep%20them%20together.%20Having%20the%20retractable%20cable%20also%20means%20that%20the%20battery%20is%20never%20a%20mess.%20I'm%20not%20wrapping%20the%20cable%20around%20it%20or%20losing%20it.%20I've%20tried%20some%20other%20power%20devices%20that%20just%20dangle%20a%20cable%20off%20the%20side.%20In%20practice%2C%20I%20much%20prefer%20the%20retractable%20cord.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20of%20an%20Anker%20Nano%20Power%20Bank%20in%20hand.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb95b4e1443b8dc48e27de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Nano%20Power%20Bank's%20screen%20shows%20you%20how%20much%20power%20is%20left%20and%20how%20long%20it%20will%20take%20to%20fully%20recharge.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Nano's%20power%20capacity%2C%20size%2C%20and%20retractable%20USB-C%20cable%20are%20the%20main%20reasons%20I%20keep%20reaching%20for%20it%20when%20I%20travel%2C%20but%20it%20has%20other%20things%20I%20like%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20it%20has%20an%20extra%20USB-C%20and%20USB-A%20port%2C%20so%20you%20can%20plug%20in%20longer%20cables%20if%20you%20prefer%2C%20or%20charge%20multiple%20devices.%20The%20power%20bank%20also%20supports%20pass-through%20charging%2C%20so%20in%20a%20hotel%20I%20can%20plug%20the%20Nano%20in%20to%20recharge%20its%20battery%20while%20still%20powering%20my%20phone%20with%20the%20retractable%20cable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126413087sjg-20%26h%3Da8ea24c9e265a6f2033070a1bbd6be61c327033252cd4916f150d1b887614b4b%26postID%3D69fb944131845c865e3bde24%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fanker-nano-power-bank-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FAnker-Power-Built-Retractable-USB-C%252Fdp%252FB0DGKWTQQC%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENano%20Power%20Bank%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20has%20an%20integrated%20display%2C%20and%20though%20this%20may%20seem%20silly%20at%20first%2C%20it's%20actually%20really%20handy.%20Mostly%2C%20I%20use%20it%20to%20see%20how%20much%20battery%20is%20left%2C%20but%20it%20can%20do%20more.%20The%20screen%20will%20show%20how%20much%20power%20a%20device%20is%20consuming%2C%20and%20you%20can%20get%20a%20sense%20of%20how%20quickly%20it%20will%20power%20up.%20I%20also%20like%20that%20the%20display%20will%20tell%20me%20how%20long%20it%20will%20take%20to%20recharge%20the%20Power%20Bank%20back%20to%20100%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImportantly%2C%20the%2010K%20Nano%20Power%20Bank%20can%20also%20provide%20up%20to%2045W%20of%20power.%20That%20means%20when%20you%20plug%