's%20first%20approach%20to%20Trump%202.0%3A%20Give%20Donald%20Trump%20what%20he%20wants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20it's%20trying%20something%20different%3A%20The%20opposite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fcc.gov%2Fecfs%2Fdocument%2F10507899614175%2F1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiling%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20federal%20government%20this%20week%2C%20Disney%20pushed%20back%20against%20its%20attempt%20to%20regulate%20which%20guests%20can%20appear%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20View%2C%26quot%3B%20calling%20those%20efforts%20%26quot%3Bunprecedented%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20threat%20to%20free%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20Disney's%20fight%20in%20this%20case%20is%20theoretically%20with%20the%20Federal%20Communications%20Commission%2C%20not%20the%20president%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20we%20should%20be%20clear%20about%20this%3A%20FCC%20head%20Brendan%20Carr%20was%20placed%20in%20the%20job%20by%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Ffeatures%2F2026-03-17%2Ftrump-s-fcc-chair-unfazed-by-south-park-parody-jimmy-kimmel-controversy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eacts%20as%20if%20he%20is%20an%20extension%20of%20Donald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20Disney%20says%20Carr's%20agency%20is%20out%20of%20line%2C%20it%20knows%20exactly%20how%20that%20critique%20is%20going%20to%20land%20in%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20the%20second%20time%20in%20weeks%20that%20Disney%20has%20taken%20on%20the%20White%20House.%20Last%20month%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmelania-trump-jimmy-kimmel-expectant-widow-joke-abc-disney-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMelania%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20then%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-wants-jimmy-kimmel-fired-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20on%20Disney's%20ABC%20to%20punish%20Jimmy%20Kimmel%20for%20a%20joke%20he'd%20made%20about%20them.%20The%20following%20day%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffcc-reviews-disney-abc-licenses-dei-policy-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECarr's%20FCC%20said%20it%20was%20reviewing%20Disney's%20broadcast%20licenses%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20years%20earlier%20than%20planned.%20But%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjimmy-kimmel-donald-trump-fight-fcc-disney-what-happens-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKimmel%20has%20stayed%20on%20the%20air%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20he%20continues%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjimmy-kimmel-melania-trump-calls-for-firing-widow-joke-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etweak%20the%20Trumps%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20clear%3A%20This%20isn't%20a%20case%20of%20Disney%2C%20or%20new%20CEO%20Josh%20D'Amaro%2C%20challenging%20Trump%20to%20a%20duel.%20But%20it%20does%20seem%20to%20be%20a%20calculated%20call%20by%20D'Amaro%3A%20He's%20decided%20to%20push%20back%2C%20politely%20but%20firmly%2C%20against%20Trump's%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that's%20a%20meaningful%20change%20from%20the%20message%20Disney%20sent%20in%20the%20first%20part%20of%20Trump's%20second%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20fall%20of%202024%20%E2%80%94%20after%20Trump's%20reelection%20but%20before%20he'd%20been%20inaugurated%20%E2%80%94%20Disney%20settled%20a%20defamation%20suit%20many%20experts%20thought%20it%20would%20easily%20win%2C%20agreeing%20to%20a%20%2415%20million%20payout%20to%20Trump%20(via%20his%20planned%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.trumplibrary.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epresidential%20library%3C%2Fa%3E).%20And%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202025%2C%20Disney%20took%20Kimmel%20off%20the%20air%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjimmy-kimmel-donald-trump-bad-why-explained-free-speech-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECarr%20complained%20about%20another%20Trump%20joke%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20host%20had%20told.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20extensive%20public%20outcry%20over%20Kimmel's%20suspension%20helped%20then-CEO%20Bob%20Iger%20change%20his%20mind%2C%20and%20he%20reinstated%20Kimmel%20after%20a%20few%20days.%20Now%20his%20successor%20seems%20to%20be%20following%20in%20his%20footsteps%20%E2%80%94%20neither%20man%20is%20critiquing%20Trump%20in%20public%2C%20but%20they're%20also%20not%20giving%20him%20what%20he%20wants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I've%20noted%20before%2C%20keeping%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjimmy-kimmel-donald-trump-fight-fcc-disney-what-happens-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKimmel%20on%20the%20air%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20Disney%20is%20immune%20to%20pressure%20from%20Trump%20and%20Carr%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20if%20you%20wanted%20to%2C%20you%20could%20argue%20that%20keeping%20Kimmel%20on%20air%2C%20but%20not%20pushing%20back%20out%20loud%20against%20Trump%2C%20isn't%20really%20pushing%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20week's%20filing%20makes%20it%20harder%20to%20make%20that%20argument.%20It's%20narrowly%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Ftv%2Ftv-news%2Fbrendan-carr-fcc-the-view-enforcement-proceedings-equal-time-1236509297%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFCC's%20%26quot%3Bequal%20time%26quot%3B%20clause%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20FCC's%20attempt%20to%20use%20that%20clause%20to%20regulate%20whether%20a%20daytime%20talk%20show%20can%20have%20certain%20political%20candidates%20on%20air%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcolbert-says-cbs-pulled-talarico-interview-fcc-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20issue%20also%20flared%20up%20a%20few%20months%20ago%20over%20on%20Paramount's%20CBS%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20its%20late-night%20show%20hosted%20by%20Stephen%20Colbert).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20language%20of%20the%20filing%2C%20which%20uses%20phrases%20like%20%26quot%3Bchill%20critical%20protected%20speech%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bthe%20danger%20is%20that%20the%20government%20will%20simply%20decide%20which%20perspectives%20to%20regulate%20and%20which%20to%20leave%20undisturbed%2C%26quot%3B%20makes%20it%20clear%20that%20Disney%20isn't%20just%20making%20a%20narrow%20technocratic%20argument%20with%20Trump's%20FCC%2C%20but%20a%20big%2C%20thematic%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20Disney%20is%20using%20Paul%20Clement%2C%20a%20well-known%20conservative%20attorney%20who%20worked%20in%20the%20George%20W%20Bush%20White%20House%20and%20has%20argued%20dozens%20of%20cases%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20is%20another%20message%3A%20%3Cem%3EWe're%20willing%20to%20fight%20this%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20with%20heavy-duty%20firepower%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20Disney%20for%20comment%20and%20was%20directed%20back%20to%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fcc.gov%2Fecfs%2Fsearch%2Fsearch-filings%2Ffiling%2F10507899614175%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFCC%20filing%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20haven't%20heard%20back%20from%20Carr.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20none%20of%20this%20means%20that%20Disney%20is%20joining%20the%20%23Resistance.%20It%20would%20rather%20not%20be%20fighting%20the%20federal%20government.%20And%20it%20definitely%20doesn't%20want%20to%20alienate%20the%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20people%20who%20voted%20for%20Trump%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20it%20wants%20to%20watch%20its%20shows%20and%20movies%2C%20and%20to%20visit%20its%20theme%20parks%20and%20cruise%20ships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20does%20look%20like%20Disney%20is%20willing%20to%20draw%20some%20discrete%20lines%20in%20the%20sand.%20That's%20a%20change%20worth%20noting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-trump-view-kimmel-damaro-iger-fcc-carr-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778270150000%2C%22visual%22%3A%2