%20investment%20arrived%20before%20Microsoft%20poured%20billions%20into%20the%20AI%20lab.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI's%20meteoric%20rise%20means%20the%20potential%20for%20huge%20windfalls%20for%20early%20investors.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUniversity%20of%20Michigan%20made%20a%20very%20good%2C%20very%20early%20bet%20on%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20running%20the%20public%20school's%20endowments%20put%20%2420%20million%20into%20one%20of%20the%20AI%20lab's%20earliest%20fundraising%20efforts%2C%20according%20to%20an%20exhibit%20in%20the%20ongoing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-trial-exposes-truth-about-workplace-texts-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%20and%20Sam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%20litigation.%20The%20University%20of%20Michigan%20moved%20in%20before%20Microsoft%20invested%20billions%20into%20OpenAI%20and%20before%20ChatGPT's%20release%20kicked%20off%20the%20modern%20AI%20boom.%20The%20Ann%20Arbor%20school%20stands%20to%20make%20a%20fortune.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20document%20is%20unclear%20about%20the%20exact%20terms%20of%20Michigan's%20stake%2C%20the%20university%20is%20sitting%20pretty.%20When%20it%20contributed%20%2420%20million%2C%20it%20set%20a%20%26quot%3Btarget%20redemption%20amount%26quot%3B%20of%20%242%20billion.%20That's%20how%20much%20the%20university%20aims%20to%20earn%20back%20from%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20university's%20%2420%20million%20stake%20arrived%20in%20the%20same%20early%20cluster%20as%20%2450%20million%20investments%20from%20Khosla%20Ventures%20and%20from%20LinkedIn%20cofounder%20Reid%20Hoffman's%20venture%20philanthropy%20fund%2C%20the%20Aphorism%20Foundation.%20The%20batch%20also%20included%20%2410%20million%20from%20a%20Y%20Combinator%20fund%20and%20%243%20million%20from%20the%20trust%20of%20Gmail%20creator%20Paul%20Buchheit.%20Microsoft's%202019%20infusion%20of%20%241%20billion%20came%20later%2C%20the%20document%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20University%20of%20Michigan%20and%20the%20other%20early%20investors%20would%20be%20prioritized%20above%20Microsoft%20in%20OpenAI's%20payout%20order%2C%20the%20document%20says.%20Their%20%26quot%3Btarget%20redemption%20amounts%26quot%3B%20also%20rise%20with%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20University%20of%20Michigan%20and%20OpenAI%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20common%20for%C2%A0endowments%20to%20invest%C2%A0with%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvc-returns-union-square-ventures-sequoia-y-combinator-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESilicon%20Valley%20venture%20capitalists%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20though%20it's%C2%A0rarer%20to%20see%20a%20direct%20stake.%20Michigan's%20total%20endowment%20is%20huge%20%E2%80%94%20valued%20at%20%2421.2%20billion%20last%20year%20%E2%80%94%20and%20has%20also%20invested%20with%20Sam%20Altman's%20and%20his%20brother%20Jack%20Altman's%20venture%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDan%20Feder%2C%20who%20leads%20the%20university%20endowment's%20venture%20capital%20and%20private%20equity%20investments%2C%20joined%20Jack%20Altman's%20podcast%20last%20June.%20Feder%20said%20that%20venture%20capital%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20pretty%20lousy%20area%20to%20invest%20unless%20you%20are%20investing%20or%20getting%20exposure%20to%20the%20underlying%20companies%20that%20really%20matter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20which%20case%20it's%20obviously%20very%20good.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20good.%20Very%2C%20very%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20Feder%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20University%20of%20Michigan%20wouldn't%20be%20the%20only%20school%20to%20make%20a%20killing%20from%20an%20early%20tech%20investment.%20In%202017%2C%20a%20Catholic%20high%20school%20in%20the%20San%20Francisco%20Bay%20Area%20made%20%2424%20million%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa-high-school-in-california-made-24-million-from-the-snap-ipo-2017-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESnap's%20IPO%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ascouncil%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Escouncil%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20or%20over%20text%2C%20Signal%2C%20Telegram%2C%20or%20WhatsApp%20at%20415-757-8198.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ECorrection%3A%20May%208%2C%202026%20%E2%80%94%20An%20earlier%20version%20of%20this%20story%20misstated%20how%20much%20a%20Catholic%20high%20school%20made%20in%20the%20Snap%20IPO.%20It%20made%20%2424%20million.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmichigan-early-openai-investment-yield-billions-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778267100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fe29ddba7ef34b41f367fa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmichigan-early-openai-investment-yield-billions-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20University%20of%20Michigan's%20early%20stake%20in%20OpenAI%2C%20before%20Microsoft's%20massive%20investment%2C%20could%20yield%20%242%20billion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22scouncil%40insider.com%20(Stephen%20Council)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Devil%20Wears%20Prada%202%E2%80%99%20Salaries%3A%20How%20Meryl%20Streep%20Landed%20a%20%2412.5%20Million%20Payday%20With%20Big%20Bonuses%20%E2%80%93%20and%20Shared%20the%20Wealth%20with%20Anne%20Hathaway%20and%20Emily%20Blunt%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778266800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236741185%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20women%20of%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Devil%20Wears%20Prada%202%E2%80%9D%20are%20clacking%20their%20stilettos%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20bank.%C2%A0%20As%20the%20sequel%20to%20the%20iconic%20fashion%20film%20continues%20to%20rake%20in%20cash%20across%20the%20globe%20%E2%80%94%20%24300%20million%20in%20box%20office%20and%20counting%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0multiple%20sources%20told%20Variety%20what%20the%20triumvirate%20of%20leading%20ladies%20earned%20to%20return%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Varietymattdonnelly%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kevin%20O'Leary%20defends%20his%20Utah%20data%20center%20project%3A%20'Think%20about%20the%20number%20of%20jobs'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223268%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kevin%20O'Leary%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fe176dc9dd4cb81cda89a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222241%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKevin%20O'Leary's%20data%20center%20campus%20in%20northwest%20Utah%20is%20facing%20resistance%20from%20the%20community%20where%20it's%20being%20built.%3Cp%3ERichard%20Shotwell%2FInvision%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EKevin%20O'Leary%20says%20people%20have%20misconceptions%20about%20what%20data%20centers%20are.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EO'Leary%20is%20building%20a%20data%20center%20in%20Utah%20despite%20community%20resistance.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EData%20center%20development%20has%20become%20a%20serious%20issue%20for%20many%20American%20communities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20Americans%20don't%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-center-industry-response-growing-pushback-regulation-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20data%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%20popping%20up%20in%20their%20communities%2C%20though%20Kevin%20O'Leary%20thinks%20that's%20because%20they%20don't%20fully%20understand%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EO'Leary%2C%20the%20venture%20capitalist%20and%20%26quot%3BShark%20Tank%26quot%3B%20investor%20who%20recently%20starred%20as%20a%20villainous%20businessman%20in%20%26quot%3BMarty%20Supreme%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Americans%20have%20misconceptions%20about%20data%20centers%20and%20their%20environmental%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20understanding%20the%20concerns%20of%20people%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20think%20about%20the%20number%20of%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Leary%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAddressing%20environmental%20worries%2C%20O'Leary%20noted%20that%20he%20graduated%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Waterloo%20with%20a%20degree%20in%20environmental%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20a%20group%20comes%20to%20me%20and%20says%2C%20'Look%2C%20I%20have%20concerns%20about%20water%2C%20I%20have%20concerns%20about%20air%2C%20I%20have%20concerns%20about%20wildlife%2C'%20I%20totally%20get%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Leary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EO'Leary%20has%20clashed%20with%20residents%20in%20Box%20Elder%20County%2C%20Utah%2C%20over%20a%20new%20AI%20data%20center%20he's%20backing%20on%20a%2040%2C000-acre%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECounty%20commissioners%20approved%20the%20project%2C%20which%20is%20also%20backed%20by%20Utah's%20Military%20Installation%20Development%20Authority%2C%20on%20Monday%20despite%20the%20community%20opposition.%20O'Leary%20said%2C%20without%20providing%20evidence%2C%20that%20the%20criticism%20mainly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkevin-oleary-blames-paid-activists-for-utah-data-center-protests-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecame%20from%20%26quot%3Bprofessional%20protesters%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20were%20%26quot%3Bpaid%20by%20somebody.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20major%20concern%20for%20residents%20about%20the%20data%20center%20%E2%80%94%20dubbed%20the%20Stratos%20Project%20%E2%80%94%20is%20that%20it%20could%20strain%20the%20water%20supply.%20Data%20centers%20can%20use%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-data-centers-are-deepening-the-water-crisis-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emillions%20of%20gallons%20of%20water%3C%2Fa%3E%20each%20day.%20Increased%20utility%20bills%2C%20noise%2C%20and%20a%20drop%20in%20quality%20of%20life%20are%20also%20points%20of%20contention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EO'Leary%20said%20the%20public%20misunderstands%20the%20impact%20of%20data%20centers%20because%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Bpoorly%20represented%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20past%2C%20and%20that%20the%20technology%20powering%20them%20has%20%26quot%3Badvanced%20dramatically.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20data%20centers%20don't%20use%20as%20much%20water%20as%20they%20once%20did%20and%20can%20use%20a%20closed-loop%20system%20to%20avoid%20evaporation.%20Data%20centers%20can%20also%20rely%20on%20air-cooled%20turbines%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20managing%20the%20temperature%20of%20the%20computer%20arrays%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20fact%20sheet%20published%20by%20Box%20Elder%20County%20said%20the%20project%20won't%20divert%20water%20from%20the%20nearby%20Great%20Salt%20Lake%2C%20agriculture%2C%20or%20homes.%20It%20also%20says%20that%20Stratos%20won't%20increase%20electricity%20prices%20or%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20residents%2C%20however%2C%20are%20not%20so%20sure.%20The%20Salt%20Lake%20Tribune%20reported%20on%20Thursday%20that%20an%20application%20to%20divert%20water%20from%20the%20Salt%20Wells%20Spring%20stream%2C%20near%20the%20Great%20Salt%20Lake%20and%20long%20used%20by%20a%20local%20ranch%20for%20irrigation%2C%20was%20rescinded%20after%20nearly%20thousands%20of%20Utah%20residents%20lodged%20complaints.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20some%20point%2C%20understanding%20the%20value%20of%20sustainability%2C%20water%20and%20air%20rights%2C%20indigenous%20rights%2C%20and%20making%20sure%20the%20constituencies%20understand%20what%20you're%20doing%20is%20going%20to%20be%20more%20valuable%20than%20the%20equity%20you%20raise%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Leary%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-centers-opposition-resistance-anjney-midha-stanford-ai-professor-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnjney%20Midha%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Stanford%20University%20adjunct%20lecturer%20who%20appeared%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BAccess%26quot%3B%20podcast%20this%20week%2C%20would%20agree%20with%20that%20sentiment.%20He%20said%20that%20listening%20to%20local%20communities%20and%20being%20transparent%20about%20the%20intentions%20and%20impacts%20of%20data%20centers%20are%20essential%20to%20making%20them%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20view%20is%20that%20if%20it's%20not%20legible%20to%20the%20public%20that%20these%20data%20centers%20and%20the%20infrastructure%20required%20to%20unblock%20this%20kind%20of%20frontier%20technology%20progress%20are%20serving%20their%20benefit%2C%20then%20it's%20not%20going%20to%20work%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Midha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20subsequent%20post%20on%20X%20on%20Friday%2C%20O'Leary%20said%20his%20project%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Btotally%20transparent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20it%20to%20be%20the%20shining%20example%20of%20how%20you%20do%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkevin-oleary-utah-data-center-stratos-opposition-water-electricity-jobs-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778266765000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fe1777e1443b8dc48e34d