ome%20time%2C%20but%20we're%20gonna%20keep%20going%20to%20acquire%20as%20much%20as%20we%20can.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223175%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anthropic%20CEO%20Dario%20Amodei%20at%20the%20company's%20developer%20conference%20in%20San%20Francisco%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fe2c85e1443b8dc48e35b4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222113%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnthropic%20CEO%20Dario%20Amodei%20at%20the%20company's%20developer%20conference%20in%20San%20Francisco%3Cp%3EAndrej%20Sokolow%2Fpicture%20alliance%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20SpaceX%20deal%20was%20announced%2C%20Anthropic%20relaxed%20several%20rate%20limits%2C%20especially%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-ai-breakthrough-vibe-coding-revolution-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClaude%20Code%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20its%20fast-growing%20AI%20coding%20service.%20That%20matters%20because%20some%20developers%20recently%20shifted%20to%20OpenAI's%20Codex%20partly%20because%20OpenAI's%20earlier%20compute%20deals%20meant%20fewer%20restrictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20heard%20versions%20of%20this%20theme%20all%20afternoon%20at%20the%20conference%3A%20startups%2C%20developers%2C%20and%20tech%20companies%20all%20need%20more%20AI%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20startup%20CEO%20told%20me%20he%20recently%20called%20a%20top%20Google%20executive%20to%20plead%20for%20more%20Gemini%20tokens%2C%20the%20core%20unit%20of%20AI%20usage%20these%20days.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20also%20ran%20into%20a%20Cursor%20executive%20who%20crossed%20his%20fingers%20and%20looked%20anxious%20waiting%20for%20the%20startup's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-cursor-coding-xai-deal-acquisition-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eown%20SpaceX%20compute%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20kick%20in.%20He%20said%20shifting%20massive%20data-center%20capacity%20between%20customers%20is%20relatively%20easy%20because%20most%20facilities%20use%20similar%20Nvidia%20GPUs.%20Indeed%2C%20Anthropic%20said%20it%20will%20have%20access%20to%20new%20SpaceX%20compute%20within%20the%20month.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20senior%20Anthropic%20executive%20privately%20admitted%20the%20company%20underestimated%20demand.%20When%20usage%20surged%20far%20faster%20than%20expected%20this%20year%2C%20they%20scrambled%20to%20respond.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20an%20incredible%20problem%20to%20have.%20If%20Anthropic's%20revenue%20growth%20continues%20at%20anything%20close%20to%20its%20current%2080x%20annual%20pace%20for%20another%20year%2C%20the%20startup%20would%20become%20one%20of%20the%20highest-revenue%20companies%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStephen%20noticed%20signs%20of%20that%20hypergrowth%20everywhere%20at%20the%20conference%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EI've%20been%20covering%20Big%20Tech%20conferences%20for%20years.%20They're%20almost%20always%20annual%2C%20with%20long-awaited%20products%20to%20peddle.%20But%20for%20Anthropic%2C%20the%20one-year%20cycle%20felt%20almost%20pointless.%20It's%20growing%20and%20shipping%20absurdly%20fast.%20I%20got%20one%20demo%20from%20someone%20who'd%20been%20here%20a%20few%20weeks%3B%20other%20workers%20told%20me%20they%20can%20barely%20keep%20up.%20Features%20are%20flipping%20from%20research%20preview%20to%20public%20beta%20in%20no%20time.%20If%20Anthropic%20can't%20teach%20its%20developers%20and%20customers%20week-in%2C%20week-out%2C%20no%20one%20will%20be%20able%20to%20follow%20along%3C%2Fem%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESign%20up%20for%20BI's%20Tech%20Memo%20newsletter%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Ftech-memo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Reach%20out%20to%20me%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%