s%20it%20was%20the%20best%20month%20since%202020.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFunds%20such%20as%20Tiger%20Global%2C%20CastleKnight%20Management%2C%20Light%20Street%2C%20and%20more%20surged.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EClaims%20of%20historic%20performance%20are%20often%20exaggerated%20on%20Wall%20Street.%20But%20April%20was%20one%20for%20the%20record%20books.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sharp%20rebound%20across%20global%20markets%20pushed%20stocks%20to%20all-time%20highs%2C%20with%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20rising%20more%20than%2010%25%20in%20April.%20Hedge%20Fund%20Research%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bhistoric%20gain%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20industry%2C%20with%20the%20average%20fund%20up%204.8%25%20%E2%80%94%20the%20second-best%20monthly%20return%20since%202009%2C%20behind%20only%20November%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20still%20there%20were%20funds%20that%20stood%20out%20for%20their%20eye-popping%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChase%20Coleman's%20Tiger%20Global%2C%20the%20long-running%20stockpicking%20firm%2C%20was%20up%2015%25%20in%20its%20flagship%20hedge%20fund%20strategy%2C%20putting%20it%20at%20roughly%203%25%20for%20the%20year%2C%20a%20person%20close%20to%20the%20New%20York-based%20firm%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Another%20of%20the%20firm's%20growth-stock-obsessed%20peers%2C%20Glen%20Kacher's%20Light%20Street%20Capital%2C%20returned%2018.2%25%20in%20April%2C%20pushing%20its%202026%20returns%20to%2011.3%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20wasn't%20just%20stockpickers%20focused%20on%20US%20tech%20companies%20that%20dominated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECastleKnight%20Management%2C%20the%20%243.6%20billion%20event-driven%20fund%20run%20by%20billionaire%20David%20Tepper's%20nephew%2C%20Aaron%20Weitman%2C%20was%20up%2021.2%25%20last%20month%20and%20has%20made%2026.9%25%20on%20the%20year.%20Kenneth%20Tropin's%20Graham%20Capital%2C%20which%20manages%20%2421.6%20billion%20in%20assets%2C%20made%206.6%25%20in%20its%20Tactical%20Trend%20strategy%20and%204.2%25%20in%20its%20Quant%20Macro%20offering%20in%20April%3B%20those%20two%20strategies%20are%20now%20up%2020.5%25%20and%2011.1%25%2C%20respectively%2C%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmerging-markets-focused%20manager%20Carrhae%20Capital%2C%20a%20London-based%20firm%20run%20by%20former%20SAC%20trader%20Ali%20Akay%2C%20was%20up%2010%25%20on%20the%20month%20through%20April%2024%20in%20the%20firm's%20long-short%20strategy.%20It%20pushed%20the%20strategy's%20year-to-date%20gains%20into%20black%2C%20with%20returns%20of%205.5%25%2C%20HSBC's%20Hedge%20Weekly%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20another%20former%20investor%20for%20Point72%20founder%20Steve%20Cohen%2C%20Angus%20Wai%2C%20has%20his%20Asia-focused%20multimanager%20firm%20firing%20on%20all%20cylinders.%20A%20person%20close%20to%20Polymer%20Capital%2C%20which%20runs%20fundamental%20and%20quant%20strategies%2C%20said%20the%20firm%20was%20up%20more%20than%207%25%20in%20April%20and%20more%20than%2015%25%20on%20the%20year.%20The%20managers%20mentioned%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cecc3315-7481-4e50-9eb3-d51fe6cff65a%5C%22%3ELiberation%20Day%20lessons%20pay%20off%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20factors%20contributed%20to%20the%20stellar%20month%20for%20hedge%20funds.%20The%20commodity%20shocks%20and%20inflation%20fears%20in%20March%20stemming%20from%20the%20US-Iran%20war%20eased%20in%20light%20of%20ceasefire%20discussions%2C%20however%20tenuous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20and%20technology%20stocks%20also%20staged%20a%20comeback%2C%20ripping%20late%20in%20the%20month%20after%20robust%20earnings%20from%20hyperscalers%20Alphabet%2C%20Amazon%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20Microsoft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20most%20funds%2C%20April%20was%20less%20about%20embracing%20a%20benign%20macro%20regime%20and%20more%20about%20monetizing%20crisis%20hedges%2C%20covering%20shorts%2C%20and%20deciding%20how%20quickly%20to%20rebuild%20equity%20risk%20into%20a%20tape%20moving%20faster%20than%20most%20risk%20frameworks%20anticipated%2C%26quot%3B%20industry%20research%20firm%20PivotalPath%20said%20in%20a%20research%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20common%20theme%20among%20outperformers%20was%20holding%20on%20to%20core%20positions%20during%20the%20chaos%20in%20March.%20One%20prime%20broker%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20client%20activity%20was%20more%20muted%2C%20focused%20on%20hedging%20rather%20than%20selling%20longs%20and%20cutting%20shorts%2C%20a%20contrast%20with%20the%20Liberation%20Day%20tariff%20mayhem%20a%20year%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20tactical%20adjustment%20was%20rewarded%2C%20PivotalPath%20noted%2C%20as%20the%20managers%20%26quot%3Bwho%20recovered%20fastest%20had%20maintained%20high-conviction%20core%20longs%20beneath%20index-level%20hedges%20through%20March%20and%20when%20ceasefire%20headlines%20improved%20the%20risk%20tone%2C%20they%20did%20not%20need%20to%20rebuild%20from%20cash.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapril-hedge-fund-performance-tiger-global-castleknight-graham-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778262931000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fdfd88e1443b8dc48e33a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapril-hedge-fund-performance-tiger-global-castleknight-graham-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hedge%20funds%20thrived%20in%20April.%20Here's%20who%20had%20double-digit%20returns%2C%20and%20how%20lessons%20from%20last%20year's%20Liberation%20Day%20chaos%20paid%20off.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bsaacks%40businessinsider.com%20(Bradley%20Saacks%2CAlex%20Morrell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Greece%20examines%20mystery%20naval%20drone%20found%20in%20Ionian%20Sea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778262805000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbrande