t-for-green-card-worth-it-h-1b-visa-holder-says-he-has-decent-money-but-can-see-parents-once-every-two-years%2Famp_articleshow%2F130965391.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20%2442%20billion%20auto%20giant%20you've%20never%20heard%20of%20is%20building%20AI%20into%20its%20factories%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Several%20Jaguar%20E-Pace%20exoskeletons%20sit%20on%20a%20Magna%20factory%20line%20ahead%20of%20their%20subchassis%20and%20motor%20manufacturing.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f8f3c6405e0cf89dc86d27%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMagna%20says%20it%20has%20expanded%20its%20AI%20use%20across%20its%20automotive%20supply%20chain.%3Cp%3EMilos%20Vujinovic%2FSOPA%20Images%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMagna%2C%20a%20supplier%20for%20global%20carmakers%2C%20uses%20AI%20to%20track%20product%20quality%2C%20equipment%2C%20and%20energy%20use.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20produces%20components%20for%20carmakers%20worldwide%2C%20including%20BYD%2C%20Toyota%2C%20Ford%2C%20and%20Hyundai.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMachine%20learning%20and%20mobile-robot%20deployment%20are%20boosting%20efficiency%20in%20its%20factories.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fmga%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMagna%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20one%20of%20those%20companies%20most%20drivers%20have%20never%20heard%20of%20%E2%80%94%20but%20have%20almost%20certainly%20interacted%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2066-year-old%20Canadian%20firm%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20automotive%20parts%20suppliers%20in%20the%20world%2C%20building%20everything%20from%20seats%20and%20mirrors%20to%20advanced%20driver-assistance%20systems%20for%20major%20car%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20supplies%20components%20to%20at%20least%2059%20global%20automakers%2C%20including%20BYD%2C%20Tesla%2C%20Hyundai%2C%20Ford%2C%20Volkswagen%2C%20and%20Xiaopeng.%20It's%20even%20hand-built%20entire%20vehicles%2C%20including%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmercedes-benz-g-wagon-g-class-pictures-details-2017-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMercedes-Benz%20G-Wagen%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20330%20manufacturing%20and%20assembly%20plants%20spanning%2028%20countries%20and%20roughly%20%2442%20billion%20in%20annual%20sales%2C%20Magna%20sits%20deep%20inside%20the%20global%20auto%20supply%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20company%20is%20embedding%20artificial%20intelligence%20across%20that%20footprint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20is%20already%20embedded%20across%20multiple%20layers%20of%20Magna's%20supply%20chain%20and%20manufacturing%20operations%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharath%20Reddy%2C%20the%20company's%20SVP%20of%20R%26amp%3BD%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20view%20it%20as%20a%20stand-alone%20technology.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2200559160-436c-45b9-abdd-094ae6ccbc38%5C%22%3EMagna's%20AI%20bets%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Grey%2C%20light%20blue%2C%20and%20yellow%20machinery%20sit%20inside%20a%20Canadian%20aluminum-making%20Magna%20factory.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f3b5729a23d20d291b520d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222862%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMagna%20is%20deploying%20a%20five-pronged%20AI%20strategy%20throughout%20its%20manufacturing%20plants.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMagna's%20AI%20investments%20focus%20on%20five%20areas%3A%20product%20quality%2C%20equipment%20maintenance%2C%20factory%20safety%2C%20energy%20reduction%2C%20and%20output%20speed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20customers%2C%20the%20most%20visible%20example%20is%20the%20AI-powered%20vision%20inspection%20system.%20Like%20the%20camera%20system%20Business%20Insider%20covered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fford-uses-ai-cameras-in-factories-prevent-recalls-costly-rework-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ein%20Ford's%20plants%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Magna%20uses%20high-resolution%20scanners%20and%20machine%20learning%20to%20detect%20parts%20defects%20and%20irregularities%20in%20real%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20gains%20from%20AI%20aren't%20coming%20from%20sweeping%2C%20end-to-end%20automation.%20Instead%2C%20Reddy%20said%20the%20clearest%20payoff%20comes%20from%20applications%20%26quot%3Bclosest%20to%20the%20physical%20operation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20key%20examples.%20Magna%20is%20using%20AI%20to%20keep%20its%20factories%20running%20more%20smoothly.%20Systems%20that%20monitor%20vibration%2C%20temperature%2C%20and%20pressure%20can%20predict%20equipment%20failures%20before%20they%20happen%2C%20helping%20plants%20avoid%20costly%20downtime.%20The%20company%20is%20also%20deploying%20autonomous%20mobile%20robots%20to%20move%20heavy%20materials%20between%20workstations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20layer%20focuses%20on%20efficiency.%20Magna%20uses%20machine%20learning%20to%20track%20energy%20use%2C%20water%20consumption%2C%20and%20industrial%20waste%20across%20facilities%2C%20flagging%20anomalies%20and%20identifying%20ways%20to%20reduce%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20Magna%20is%20also%20working%20toward%20what%20it%20calls%20a%20%26quot%3Bunified%20factory%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20data%2C%20software%2C%20and%20automation%20systems%20are%20connected%20across%20factory-wide%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%20is%20that%20the%20unified%20system's%20value%20is%20more%20diffuse%2C%20Reddy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20shows%20up%20across%20scheduling%2C%20material%20flow%2C%20and%20decision-making%20rather%20than%20in%20a%20single%20metric%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20value%20is%20real%2C%20but%20it's%20more%20distributed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221a5f30d6-235d-437c-ade0-aff446287fbd%5C%22%3EAI%20that%20helps%20predict%20global%20risk%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Four%20workers%20in%20red%20polo%20shirts%20stand%20together%20at%20a%20Magna%20factory%20next%20to%20a%20work%20station.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f5072d9a23d20d291b5949%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223071%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMagna%20says%20AI%20is%20also%20helping%20to%20adjust%20to%20global%20risks%20faster.%3Cp%3EMilos%20Vujinovic%2FSOPA%20Images%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20auto%20industry%20has%20been%20hit%20by%20years%20of%20disruption%20%E2%80%94%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-raises-tariffs-european-cars-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etariffs%20and%20trade%20tensions%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20material%20supply%20shortages%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fev-shakeout-us-market-tesla-toyota-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Euneven%20global%20EV%20demand%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAutomakers%20have%20deployed%20news-monitoring%20models%20to%20help%20adjust%20to%20that%20unevenness.%20For%20example%2C%20last%20year%2C%20Business%20Insider%20reported%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-gm-uses-ai-predict-prevent-costly-supply-chain-disruptions-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGeneral%20Motors%20uses%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20monitor%20disruptions%20to%20its%20global%20supply%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReddy%20said%20Magna%20has%20a%20similar%20approach.%20AI%20doesn't%20replace%20%26quot%3Bthe%20fundamentals%20of%20supply%20chain%20management%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Instead%2C%20it%20acts%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bamplifier%26quot%3B%20for%20potential%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20near-term%20impact%20will%20be%20better%20visibility%20and%20faster%20decision-making%20%E2%80%94%20earlier%20signals%2C%20stronger%20scenario%20modeling%2C%20and%20more%20coordinated%20response%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20a%20single%20breakthrough%2C%20Magna's%20factories%20are%20becoming%20more%20software-defined%20step%20by%20step%20%E2%80%94%20with%20intelligence%20layered%20into%20the%20parts%20of%20the%20system%20where%20it%20can%20reliably%20deliver%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauto-giant-magna-ai-factories-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778261518000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f8f3c6405e0cf89dc86d27%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauto-giant-magna-ai-factories-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Magna%20builds%20parts%20for%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20biggest%20automakers%2C%20like%20BYD%2C%20Ford%2C%20and%20Toyota.%20It%20has%20a%20five-pronged%20AI%20strategy%20for%20its%20plants.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bshimkus%40insider.com%20(Ben%20Shimkus)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Return%20of%20Palestine%20Marathon%20attracts%20thousands%20of%20runners%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778261008000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fdf3a%2Flive%2F27ff0570-4ad5-11f1-ac78-2112837ce2aa.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fcm2p4n000pko%233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Thousands%20of%20people%20have%20taken%20part%20in%20the%20Palestine%20Marathon%2C%20which%20returns%20to%20Bethlehem%20after%20a%20two-year%20pause%20over%20the%20Gaza%20War.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A91%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fcm2p4n000pko%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22titl