country-why-immigrants-are-choosing-voluntarily-departure-over-detention-or-asylum-in-us%2Farticleshow%2F130964715.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fid-rather-die-in-my-country-why-immigrants-are-choosing-voluntarily-departure-over-detention-or-asylum-in-us%2Famp_articleshow%2F130964715.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fid-rather-die-in-my-country-why-immigrants-are-choosing-voluntarily-departure-over-detention-or-asylum-in-us%2Famp_articleshow%2F130964715.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AI%20capex%20is%20coming%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20a%20crucial%20pillar%20for%20stock%20gains%2C%20Goldman%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227764%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22NYSE%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fddf59ba7ef34b41f3650d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225176%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EANGELA%20WEISS%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20capex%20is%20surging%2C%20but%20it's%20eating%20into%20share%20buybacks%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs%20say.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHyperscalers%20have%20seen%20a%20dramatic%20decline%20in%20buyback%20activity.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThe%20AI%20investment%20boom%20will%20drive%20a%20continued%20shift%20from%20buybacks%20to%20capex%20for%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analysts%20wrote.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20are%20spending%20billions%20investing%20in%20AI%2C%20but%20it's%20coming%20at%20a%20cost%3A%20They're%20buying%20back%20shares%20at%20slower%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20outlined%20that%20as%20AI%20capex%20grows%2C%20companies%20buying%20back%20shares%20at%20a%20slower%20rate.%20The%20hyperscalers%20that%20are%20leading%20AI%20spending%2C%20are%20seeing%20share%20buyback%20growth%20slow%20at%20a%20more%20dramatic%20rate%2C%20a%20drag%20on%20the%20broader%20market's%20buyback%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20AI%20investment%20boom%20will%20drive%20a%20continued%20shift%20from%20buybacks%20to%20capex%20for%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analysts%20wrote.%20Share%20buybacks%20are%20typically%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-buyback-outlook-trillion-dollar-support-fight-further-crash-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebullish%20for%20a%20stock%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20provide%20support%20for%20stocks%20when%20companies%20see%20their%20shares%20as%20undervalued.%20Buybacks%20also%20reduce%20the%20amount%20of%20shares%20in%20the%20market%2C%20boosting%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FgQQrv%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22538%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20projects%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20capex%20to%20grow%2033%25%20in%202026%20while%20gross%20buybacks%20grow%20only%203%25.%20For%20comparison%2C%20capex%20growth%20sat%20at%2020%25%20and%20buybacks%20grew%209%25%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-earnings-winners-losers-ai-capex-cloud-meta-goog-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EQ1%20earnings%20season%3C%2Fa%3E%20highlighted%20the%20ongoing%20rotation%20from%20buybacks%20to%20capex%20and%20R%26amp%3BD.%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20capex%20growth%20is%20tracking%20at%20%2B39%25%20during%20Q1%20compared%20with%20%2B1%25%20for%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20gross%20buybacks%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analysts%20laid%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20dynamic%20of%20share%20buyback%20growth%20stalling%20as%20capex%20growth%20intensifies%20is%20more%20pronounced%20for%20the%20Big%20Tech%20names%20leading%20the%20AI%20spending%20spree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22baabceb6-df55-41e3-8d03-2f9f8d7df0c3%5C%22%3EBig%20Tech%20sees%20a%20more%20dramatic%20drop%20off%20in%20buybacks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20hyperscalers%20like%20Amazon%2C%20Google%2C%20Meta%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20Oracle%2C%20are%20expected%20to%20spend%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-earnings-microsoft-ai-investment-capex-plan-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%24755%20billion%20in%20capex%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202026%2C%20an%2083%25%20year-over-year%20jump%2C%20according%20to%20Goldman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsensus%20estimates%20show%20hyperscaler%20capex%20amounting%20to%20100%25%20of%20cash%20flows%20from%20operations%20this%20year%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20leaves%20little%20room%20to%20return%20cash%20to%20shareholders%20without%20a%20sharp%20deceleration%20in%20capex%20growth%2C%20a%20large%20drawdown%20of%20cash%20balances%2C%20or%20a%20major%20increase%20in%20debt%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analysts%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226f38a5d3-9897-4ecf-b454-882f9be834e8%5C%22%3EHyperscalers%20have%20pulled%20back%20back%20on%20buybacks%20and%20dividends%20while%20spending%20big%20on%20AI%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22905%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hyperscalers%20pull%20back%20on%20share%20buybacks%20and%20dividends%20as%20AI%20capex%20surges.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fdf1a3e1443b8dc48e3343%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22722%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChart%20shows%20large%20hyperscalers%2C%20specifically%20Amazon%2C%20Alphabet%2C%20Meta%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20Oracle%2C%20for%20the%20trailing%20four%20quarters%20through%20Q1%202026.%3Cp%3EGoldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20group%20now%20allocates%2015%25%20of%20total%20cash%20spending%20on%20buybacks%20compared%20with%20an%20average%20of%2027%25%20from%202017-2022.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202025%2C%20Amazon%2C%20Google%2C%20Meta%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20Oracle%20alone%20accounted%20for%20more%20than%20a%20third%20(34%25)%20of%20the%20capex%20and%20R%26amp%3BD%20of%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%2C%20while%20only%20making%20up%2010%25%20of%20buybacks%20and%20dividends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20expects%20this%20hyperscaler%20dynamic%20to%20continue%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3BReduced%20buyback%20activity%20among%20the%20hyperscalers%20will%20weigh%20on%20aggregate%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20buybacks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20noted%20that%20some%20of%20the%20buyback%20headwinds%20from%20hyperscalers%20could%20be%20offset%20by%20an%20uptick%20in%20buyback%20from%20the%20beneficiaries%20of%20Big%20Tech's%20AI%20spending%2C%20like%20chipmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-spending-capex-big-tech-stocks-share-buybacks-market-investing-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778259099000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fddf77ba7ef34b41f3650e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-spending-capex-big-tech-stocks-share-buybacks-market-investing-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Capital%20expenditures%20growth%20has%20skyrocketed%20in%20the%20AI%20era%2C%20but%20it's%20come%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20share%20buybacks%20and%20dividends%2C%20Goldman%20says%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nbuchanan%40insider.com%20(Naomi%20Buchanan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Details%20Of%20Prison%20Killing%3A%20Prosecutors%20outline%20Ian%20Watkins%20attack%3B%20UK%20inmates%20face%20murder%20charge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778258405000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-130964521%2Cimgsize-29046.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia