0with%20growth%20driven%20by%20viral%20menu%20hits%2C%20a%20focus%20on%20value%2C%20and%20a%20back-to-basics%20strategy.%3Cp%3EChili's%20Grill%20%26amp%3B%20Bar%3B%20Robert%20V%20Schwemmer%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChili's%20is%20outperforming%20casual-dining%20rivals%20like%20Applebee's%20and%20Red%20Lobster%20in%20sales%20and%20traffic%20growth.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECEO%20Kevin%20Hochman%20credits%20a%20simple%20formula%3A%20%26quot%3BMarketing%20brings%20them%20in%3B%20ops%20brings%20them%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20chain's%20focus%20on%20fundamentals%20and%20value%20is%20driving%20its%20turnaround%2C%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EChili's%20has%20pulled%20off%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-americans-are-dining-chilis-sweetgreen-mcdonalds-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebiggest%20turnarounds%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20casual%20dining%2C%20and%20CEO%20Kevin%20Hochman%20says%20the%20strategy%20behind%20it%20isn't%20complicated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chain%20has%20had%20steady%20sales%20growth%20over%20the%20past%20four%20years%20since%20Hochman%20took%20over%20as%20president%20of%20parent%20company%20Brinker%20International%2C%20which%20also%20owns%20the%20Italian%20casual-dining%20chain%20Maggiano's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20two%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Hochman%20told%20Business%20Insider%20of%20the%20company's%20growth.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20saying%20here%3A%20marketing%20brings%20them%20in%2C%20and%20ops%20brings%20them%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20flashy%20ads%20and%20viral%20menu%20items%20like%20the%20chain's%20cheese-pulling%20mozzarella%20sticks%20and%20Triple%20Dipper%20appetizer%20combo%2C%20which%20accounted%20for%2014%25%20of%20Chili's%20total%20sales%20in%20early%202025%2C%20are%20a%20good%20way%20to%20bring%20customers%20through%20the%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227281%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22chilis%20mozzarella%20cheese%20pull%20triple%20dipper%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fa3023b3045b292f636fd0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225461%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChili's%20has%20leaned%20into%20marketing%20and%20operations%20to%20drive%20growth.%3Cp%3EChili's%20Grill%20%26amp%3B%20Bar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHochman%20said%20these%20kinds%20of%20organic%20trends%20are%20a%20key%20part%20of%20the%20brand's%20marketing%20engine%2C%20noting%20that%20viral%20posts%20from%20microinfluencers%20and%20content%20creators%20can%20often%20drive%20new%20customers%20to%20try%20the%20items%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20marketing%20has%20to%20be%20exciting%2C%26quot%3B%20Hochman%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20the%20operators%20are%20in%20charge%20of%20creating%20that%20experience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a22d23b7-a65c-46f4-a5f0-153e6c99b8c2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFocusing%20on%20the%20fundamentals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHocham%20isn't%20focused%20on%20chasing%20gimmicks%20like%20drone%20delivery%2C%20which%20chains%20like%20Dave's%20Hot%20Chicken%20and%20Chipotle%20have%20been%20experimenting%20with%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.restaurantbusinessonline.com%2Ftechnology%2Fsearch-perfect-delivery-some-restaurants-look-skies%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERestaurant%20Business%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20Instead%2C%20Hochman%20said%20his%20focus%20is%20on%20the%20fundamentals%20that%20make%20the%20in-restaurant%20experience%20attractive%20to%20new%20and%20returning%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20includes%20food%20quality%2C%20speedy%20service%2C%20clean%20restaurants%2C%20and%20a%20seamless%20checkout%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHochman%20said%20some%20of%20those%20changes%20included%20a%20new%20seasoning%20shaker%20with%20larger%20holes%20to%20cut%20down%20on%20the%20time%20it%20takes%20to%20season%20fries%2C%20simplifying%20the%20menu%20to%20improve%20consistency%2C%20and%20using%20iPads%20to%20improve%20order%20accuracy%20and%20speed%20up%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20the%20things%20nobody%20talks%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20everyday%20stuff%2C%20that%20makes%20us%20better%20and%20better%2C%20that's%20kind%20of%20been%20our%20secret%20sauce.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsistent%20execution%20at%20the%20operational%20level%20means%20food%20customers%20receive%20in%20restaurants%20matches%20what%20they%20see%20in%20ads%20and%20on%20social%20media%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20see%20the%20burger%20or%20chicken%20sandwich%20for%20%2410.99%20on%20the%20screen%2C%20and%20the%20fries%20are%20crisp%20and%20hot%20and%20steaming%20with%20seasoning%2C%20and%20then%20you%20come%20in%2C%20and%20it%20looks%20exactly%20like%20that%E2%80%A6%20you're%20like%2C%20'Wow%2C%20that%20was%20a%20great%20value.%20I'm%20going%20to%20come%20back%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222f938e0d-11b0-486d-9347-fcb6214124c9%5C%22%3EDefying%20industry%20trends%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Florida%2C%20Orlando%2C%20Chili's%20Grill%20%26amp%3B%20Bar%2C%20restaurant%20entrance.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6674d2db423319f0c37239af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChili's%20is%20outperforming%20casual-dining%20rivals%20like%20Applebee's%20and%20Red%20Lobster.%3Cp%3EJeffrey%20Greenberg%2FEducation%20Images%2FUniversal%20Images%20Group%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20most%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fs21.q4cdn.com%2F420141687%2Ffiles%2Fdoc_financials%2F2026%2Fq3%2FBRINKER-INTERNATIONAL-REPORTS-THIRD-QUARTER-OF-FISCAL-2026-RESULTS-AND-UPDATES-FISCAL-2026-GUIDANCE-2026.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearnings%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20released%20on%20April%2029%2C%20Chili's%20said%20comparable%20restaurant%20sales%20rose%204%25%20in%20Q3%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20same%20quarter%20in%202025%2C%20building%20on%20a%2031%25%20jump%20a%20year%20earlier%20and%20extending%20its%20streak%20to%2020%20consecutive%20quarters%20of%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20performance%20stands%20in%20contrast%20to%20much%20of%20the%20casual-dining%20sector%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20though%20some%20chains%20that%20previously%20struggled%20are%20now%20beginning%20to%20show%20signs%20of%20a%20turnaround%20of%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Applebee's%20reported%20a%200.4%25%20decline%20in%20comparable%20domestic%20same-store%20sales%20for%20Q4%2C%20but%20sales%20rose%201.3%25%20for%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERed%20Robin%20also%20reported%20a%200.3%25%20year-over-year%20decrease%20in%20comparable%20restaurant%20revenue%20in%202025.%20However%2C%20the%20chain's%20adjusted%20earnings%20before%20interest%2C%20taxes%2C%20depreciation%2C%20and%20amortization%20were%20up%2053%25%20from%20fiscal%20year%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20competitors%20have%20leaned%20on%20heavy%20discounting%2C%20increased%20menu%20innovation%2C%20or%20buzzy%20deals%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-endless-shrimp-returns-but-hype-faded-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERed%20Lobster's%20Endless%20Shrimp%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobsters-new-lobsterfest-menu-review-photos-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELobsterfest%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20drive%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20that%20strategy%20is%20working%20%E2%80%94%20Red%20Lobster's%20CEO%2C%20Damola%20Adamolekun%2C%20reported%20in%20February%202026%20that%20sales%20are%20up%2010%25%20year%20over%20year%20after%20the%20chain%20declared%20bankruptcy%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225624367e-5c75-4676-a217-02d1a2d27629%5C%22%3ETaking%20on%20its%20rivals%20in%20the%20value%20wars%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22chilis%20big%20crispy%20chicken%20sandwich%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fa2dd5405e0cf89dc87419%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChili's%20most%20recent%20marketing%20push%20asked%20guests%20to%20compare%20its%20chicken%20sandwich%20with%20a%20fast-food%20rival's.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20fight%20to%20retain%20loyal%20customers%2C%20Chili's%20has%20also%20encouraged%20diners%20to%20compare%20its%20products%20directly%20with%20its%20competitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-chilis-vs-mcdonalds-classic-chicken-sandwich-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epop-up%20event%20in%20April%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20chain%20asked%20attendees%20to%20compare%20its%20crispy%20chicken%20sandwich%20%E2%80%94%20now%20available%20in%20more%20flavors%20and%20as%20part%20of%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrying-chilis-meal-deals-3-for-me-combos-worth-it-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%2410.99%203-For-Me%20meal%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bfast%20food%20rival%2C%26quot%3B%20identifiable%20as%20McDonald's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20go%20to%20a%20competitor%20and%20the%20same%20burger%20is%20a%20dollar%20less%20than%20ours%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't%20look%20like%20it%20did%20in%20the%20ad%2C%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20whether%20it%20was%20a%20dollar%20less%2C%26quot%3B%20Hochman%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIn%20my%20mind%2C%20that's%20money%20I%20should%20have%20spent%20somewhere%20else.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20can%20have%20a%20superior%20product%20that%20tastes%20great%20and%20is%20a%20great%20value%2C%20people%20are%20going%20to%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20if%20we%20can%20execute%20it%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20come%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchilis-ceo-how-chain-made-major-comeback-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778257074000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fccc32c9dd4cb81cda8315%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchilis-ceo-how-chain-made-major-comeback-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chili's%20is%20defying%20a%20casual-dining%20slowdown%20with%20growth%20driven%20by%20viral%20menu%20hits%2C%20a%20focus%20on%20value%2C%20and%20a%20back-to-basics%20strategy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22emcdowell%40businessinsider.com%20(Erin%20McDowell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Passenger%20from%20'Hanta%20virus'%20cruise%20visited%20school%20on%20remotest%20island%20Tristan%20de%20Cunha%2C%20believed%20to%20be%20infected%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778256920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-130964278%2Cimgsize-106932.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fpassenger-from-hanta-virus-cruise-visited-school-on-remotest-island-tristan-de-cunha-believed-to-be-infected%2Farticleshow%2F130964204.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F130964204.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A92%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fpassenger-from-hanta-virus-cruise-visited-school-on-remotest-island-tristan-de-cunha-believed-to-be-infected%2Farticleshow%2F130964204.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fpassenger-from-hanta-virus-cruise-visited-school-on-remotest-island-tristan-de-cunha-believed-to-be-infected%2Famp_articleshow%2F130964204.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fpassenger-from-hanta-virus-cruise-visited-school-on-remotest-island-tristan-de-cunha-believed-to-be-infected%2Famp_articleshow%2F130964204.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I've%20lived%20in%20Spain%20for%207%20years%20now.%20My%20daily%20schedule%20and%20social%20life%20are%20so%20different%20from%20what%20they%20were%20in%20the%20US.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20smiling%2C%20posing%20in%20front%20of%20blue%20door%20on%20white%20building%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb591de3f2a46ca8fcf89b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20I%20moved%20from%20the%20United%20States%20to%20Spain%2C%20many%20parts%20of%20my%20daily%20schedule%20and%20social%20life%20changed%20so%20much.%3Cp%3EKiersten%20Brown%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-moved-to-spain-30s-still-here-years-later-madrid-2026-3%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoved%20to%20Spain%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20US%20about%20seven%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20it's%20shifted%20so%20many%20parts%20of%20my%20life.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%2C%20my%20lunches%20are%20later%20and%20savored%20with%20company.%20Dinners%20are%20also%20late%20and%20very%20social.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20love%20how%20Spain%20prioritizes%20connection%2C%20and%20how%20taking%20a%20vacation%20feels%20like%20a%20true%20priority%20here.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-moved-from-us-to-spain-started-business-no-regrets-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoved%20from%20California%20to%20Spain%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202019%2C%20I%20knew%20my%20life%20would%20change%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20didn't%20expect%20how%20deeply%20it%20would%20shift%20the%20way%20I%20moved%20through%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20first%20few%20weeks%20as%20a%20language%20assistant%2C%20a%20Spanish%20teacher%20I%20worked%20with%20invited%20me%20for%20a%20drink%20in%20Cartagena's%20city%20center%20on%20a%20Thursday%20afternoon.%20As%20we%20walked%20through%20the%20marble%20streets%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20see%20the%20plaza%20filled%20with%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20restaurants%20and%20bars%20being%20packed%2C%20the%20streets%20themselves%20were%20buzzing%20with%20couples%20on%20benches%2C%20families%20walking%20with%20no%20particular%20destination%2C%20and%20friends%20lingering%20at%20terrace%20tables.%20It%20felt%20like%20everyone%20had%20gathered%20for%20an%20event%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20workday%2C%20but%20there%20wasn't%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20just%20how%20people%20often%20spent%20their%20free%20time%20%E2%80%94%20outside%2C%20together%2C%20and%20unhurried.%20Even%20years%20later%2C%20there's%20still%20so%20much%20of%20this%20local%20lifestyle%20I'm%20happily%20learning%20to%20embrace.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22847269ab-9653-4e4d-9627-e7980216cb5d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20took%20me%20a%20while%20to%20get%20used%20to%20having%20more%20slow%2C%20meaningful%20meals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221177%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Large%20bowl%20of.%20yellow%20rice%2C%20veggies%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb5963f9e4752b6d6015ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22883%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20Spain%2C%20I've%20been%20able%20to%20slow%20down%20and%20enjoy%20good%20company%20and%20food.%3Cp%3EKiersten%20Brown%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20workday%20lunches%20are%20typically%20a%20quick%20affair.%20It's%20common%20for%20people%20to%20head%20out%20for%20a%20quick%2C%2030-minute%20meal%20or%20just%20scarf%20down%20something%20simple%2C%20like%20a%20sandwich%20and%20chips%2C%20at%20their%20desk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-is-dinner-so-late-in-spain-2017-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELunchtime%20in%20Spain%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20far%20different%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20first%20times%20I%20noticed%20was%20while%20I%20was%20working%20at%20an%20elementary%20school.%20From%2011%3A30%20a.m.%20to%20noon%2C%20during%20the%20kids'%20recess%2C%20I'd%20head%20to%20the%20staff%20room%20with%20my%20Tupperware%20of%20pasta%20for%20lunch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20day%2C%20a%20fellow%20teacher%20stared%20at%20me%20with%20the%20most%20confused%20look%2C%20then%20calmly%20asked%20if%20I%20was%20planning%20to%20eat%20%3Cem%3Eeverything%3C%2Fem%3E%20I%20had%20brought.%20I%20was%20taken%20aback%2C%20since%20I%20wasn't%20sure%20what%20else%20I%20could've%20packed%20to%20tide%20me%20over%20until%20school%20ended%20at%202%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20didn't%20yet%20know%20was%20that%20recess%20is%20actually%20a%20time%20for%20teachers%20to%20have%20a%20light%20snack%2C%20or%20%26quot%3Baperitivo.%26quot%3B%20For%20my%20colleagues%2C%20lunch%20is%20later%2C%20starting%20after%20work%20at%202%20p.m.%2C%20so%20it's%20not%20rushed%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%2C%20it%20stretches%20until%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20shifting%20my%20eating%20schedule%2C%20I%20realized%20again%20just%20how%20different%20this%20meal%20is%20here%20when%20my%20friend%20invited%20me%20over%20for%20lunch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20arrived%2C%20her%20table%20was%20lined%20with%20small%20bowls%20of%20olives%2C%20bread%2C%20and%20olive%20oil.%20After%20snacking%2C%20our%20main%20course%20was%20served%3A%20yellow%20rice%20mixed%20with%20vegetables%2C%20similar%20to%20a%20paella.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20food%20was%20delicious%2C%20but%20the%20most%20memorable%20part%20of%20the%20meal%20was%20how%20we%20spent%20the%20time%20together.%20Our%20focus%20wasn't%20on%20eating%2C%20and%20there%20was%20no%20sense%20of%20urgency%20to%20get%20back%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20food%20was%20the%20reason%20we%20gathered%2C%20the%20company%2C%20the%20conversations%2C%20and%20the%20laughter%20truly%20completed%20the%20meal%20and%20made%20time%20slow%20down.%20This%20was%20the%20most%20present%20I%20had%20ever%20felt%20at%20a%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20salads%20topped%20with%20fruit%2C%20dressing%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb5850e3f2a46ca8fcf88f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThese%20days%2C%20I%20don't%20try%20to%20rush%20when%20I%20prepare%20and%20eat%20lunch.%3Cp%3EKiersten%20Brown%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20when%20I%20have%20lunch%20with%20my%20Spanish%20partner%2C%20it's%20an%20intentional%20break%20in%20the%20day%20that%20lasts%20about%20two%20hours%20from%20prep%20to%20finish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20often%20put%20together%20a%20salad%20with%20seasonal%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20that's%20drizzled%20with%20top-notch%20extra-virgin%20olive%20oil.%20My%20partner%20usually%20cooks%20something%20garlic-rich%2C%20like%20pollo%20al%20ajillo%20(garlic%20chicken).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaking%20time%20to%20prepare%20the%20food%20helps%20us%20slow%20down%20and%20use%20the%20meal%20to%20connect%20with%20each%20other%20and%20disconnect%20from%20the%20busyness%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDinner%20in%20Spain%20carries%20the%20same%20intentionality%20as%20lunch%20%E2%80%94%20slow%2C%20social%2C%20and%20designed%20to%20foster%20genuine%20connections.%20Whenever%20I%20dine%20out%20with%20friends%2C%20time%20becomes%20irrelevant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-flags-of-a-bad-spanish-restaurant-jose-pizarro-2019-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESpanish%20restaurants%3C%2Fa%3E%20typically%20start%20filling%20up%20around%209%3A30%20p.m.%2C%20and%20the%20tradition%20of%20%26quot%3Bsobremesa%26quot%3B%20kicks%20in%20%E2%80%94%20people%20linger%20at%20the%20table%20long%20after%20the%20meal%20ends%2C%20enjoying%20drinks%2C%20conversation%2C%20and%20connection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c3dced14-170e-4959-a93e-98a4e47d2ab0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EVacations%20have%20also%20become%20a%20priority%20and%20a%20typical%20part%20of%20life%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aerial%20view%20of%20buildings%20in%20Spain%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb5850f9e4752b6d6015df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETaking%20a%20vacation%20doesn't%20feel%20like%20such%20a%20big%20deal%20here.%3Cp%3EKiersten%20Brown%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Spain%2C%20vacation%20time%20feels%20like%20an%20essential%20part%20of%20the%20year.%20Part%20of%20it%20is%20that%2C%20generally%2C%20full-time%20workers%20here%20are%20legally%20entitled%20to%20at%20least%2030%20calendar%20days%20of%20paid%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20by%20contrast%2C%20there's%20no%20federally%20mandated%20minimum%2C%20so%20PTO%20varies%20widely.%20The%20average%20private-sector%20employee%20receives%20about%2011%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funlimited-vacation-pto-wins-risks-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epaid%20vacation%20days%3C%2Fa%3E%20(plus%20several%20paid%20sick%20days)%20after%20one%20year%20on%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-moved-to-italy-living-better-less-money-retirement-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eliving%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20extra%20paid%20time%20off%20was%20something%20I%20had%20to%20earn%20after%20hours%20and%20hours%20of%20work.%20Although%20I%20was%20adamant%20about%20taking%20all%20of%20my%20vacation%20days%2C%20not%20everyone%20I%20worked%20with%20did%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20during%20late%20July%20and%20August%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20region%20of%20Andaluc%C3%ADa%20where%20I%20live%2C%20it's%20not%20uncommon%20to%20walk%20through%20the%20city%20and%20find%20several%20shops%20and%20stores%20closed.%20Many%20people%20are%20simply%20on%20vacation%2C%20often%20for%20two-%20or%20three-week%20stretches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20city%20empties%2C%20it%20reminds%20me%20to%20unplug%20too.%20Whether%20it's%20spending%20hours%20at%20the%20beach%2C%20taking%20a%20trip%2C%20or%20allowing%20myself%20a%20day%20without%20plans%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcountry-i-return-to-every-year-spain-frequent-traveler%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESpain's%20vacation%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20taught%20me%20to%20slow%20down%2C%20cherish%20downtime%2C%20and%20focus%20on%20being%20present%20rather%20than%20busy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222e551be0-3bd6-46ac-84d0-955539cee777%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAll%20in%20all%2C%20Spain's%20slow%20pace%20has%20helped%20my%20life%20feel%20richer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20smiling%20next%20to%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb58505edd94d1e7339c4d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI've%20shifted%20my%20routines%20while%20living%20in%20Spain.%3Cp%3EKiersten%20Brown%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-american-family-made-moving-to-spain-leaving-us-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELiving%20in%20Spain%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20made%20me%20appreciate%20the%20simple%20moments%20in%20life.%20Meals%20are%20less%20about%20calories%20and%20more%20about%20connection.%20Vacations%20aren't%20a%20break%20from%20life%20but%20a%20vital%