c%20solution%20on%20the%20table.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A91%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc99lpn9ze8ro%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20AI-pilled%20CEO's%20memo%20cutting%20over%2021%25%20of%20the%20company%20is%20a%20prime%20example%20of%20the%20new%20layoffs%20playbook%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224506%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22DeepL%20CEO%20Jarek%20Kutylowski%20is%20pictured.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fdefbbc9dd4cb81cda8819%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223004%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDeepL%20CEO%20Jarek%20Kutylowski's%20layoff%20memo%20references%20tech's%20favorite%20buzzwords.%3Cp%3EBig%20Event%20Media%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20HumanX%20Conference%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDeepL%20laid%20off%20250%20employees.%20CEO%20Jarek%20Kutylowski's%20memo%20referenced%20AI%2C%20smaller%20teams%2C%20fewer%20layers%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-everyone-in-tech-talking-founder-mode-paul-graham-chesky-2024-9%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efounder%20mode%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20currently%20living%20through%20a%20massive%20structural%20shift%2C%26quot%3B%20Kutylowski%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThat%20shift%20is%20because%20of%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELayoff%20memos%20are%20starting%20to%20look%20more%20similar.%20The%20DeepL%20message%20is%20a%20prime%20example.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20the%20new%20normal%20for%20a%20company%20whose%20CEO%20is%20all%20in%20on%20AI%20and%20cutting%20jobs%20as%20a%20result%3F%20Look%20no%20further%20than%20DeepL's%20layoffs%20memo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeepl-translation-startup-close-to-raising-new-round-from-ivp-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGerman%20AI%20translation%20startup%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently%20cut%20about%20250%20employees%2C%20over%2021%25%20of%20staff.%20In%20his%20message%20posted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fpulse%2Fimportant-update-deepl-jarek-kutylowski-66yxe%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20LinkedIn%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20founder%20Jarek%20Kutylowski%20checked%20all%20the%20boxes%20for%20the%20new-age%20layoff%20memo%3A%20smaller%20teams%2C%20fewer%20management%20layers%2C%20more%20AI%2C%20and%20the%20old%20reliable%20%26quot%3Bfounder%20mode.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecent%20layoffs%20at%20Block%2C%20Atlassian%2C%20and%20more%20have%20taken%20a%20similar%20tack.%20The%20layoff%20playbook%20is%20here%20%E2%80%94%20and%20DeepL%20is%20the%20latest%20exemplar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22deb5e287-d6b2-4d22-9f29-25eafe389584%5C%22%3EBreaking%20down%20DeepL's%20layoff%20memo%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKutylowski%20began%20his%20note%20by%20introducing%20the%20layoffs%2C%20calling%20it%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20difficult%20I've%20had%20to%20make%20in%20my%20career.%26quot%3B%20He%20thanked%20the%20staff%20members%20he's%20laying%20off%20for%20their%20work%20before%20launching%20into%20his%20state%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20currently%20living%20through%20a%20massive%20structural%20shift%20in%20what%20work%20exists%2C%20who%20does%20it%2C%20and%20how%20many%20people%20it%20takes%20to%20do%20it%20well%2C%20and%20that%20shift%20is%20because%20of%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20Kutylowski%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKutylowski%20framed%20DeepL%20as%20a%20leader.%20While%20most%20companies%20have%20recognized%20the%20AI-driven%20shift%2C%20few%20have%20acted%20on%20it%2C%20he%20wrote.%20Companies%20making%20moves%20like%20DeepL%20will%20%26quot%3Bdefine%20the%20next%20decade%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20Kutylowski%20riffed%20on%20one%20of%20the%20era's%20biggest%20buzzwords%3A%20%26quot%3BAI-native.%26quot%3B%20He%20wrote%20that%20AI%20needed%20to%20be%20embedded%20deep%20within%20the%20organization%2C%20similar%20to%20Jack%20Dorsey's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjack-dorsey-block-ai-managers-player-coaches-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereorganization%20of%20Block%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20takes%20the%20pressure%20off%20of%20the%20hierarchical%20structure%20and%20team%20boundaries%20that%20have%20plagued%20companies%20for%20decades%2C%20allowing%20smaller%20groups%20-%20sometimes%20even%20an%20individual%20-%20to%20do%20work%20that%20once%20required%20entire%20teams%2C%26quot%3B%20Kutylowski%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20sounds%20familiar.%20Meta%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20mentioned%20that%20one%20employee%20could%20handle%20a%20team's%20work%20with%20AI%20during%20Meta's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-says-ai-letting-one-employee-do-work-of-teams-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJanuary%20earnings%20call%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Coinbase%20CEO%20Brian%20Armstrong%20also%20mentioned%20is%20experimenting%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoinbase-layoffs-ai-brian-armstrong-job-cuts-letter-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bone%20person%20teams%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20memo%20announcing%20a%2014%25%20reduction%20in%20head%20count%20and%20a%20maximum%20of%20five%20management%20layers%20below%20its%20C-suite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKutylowski%20also%20discussed%20the%20need%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Ftiny-teams%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmaller%20teams%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20fewer%20layers%20of%20management.%20Then%2C%20he%20hit%20on%20one%20of%20the%20tech%20industry's%20long-favorite%20slogans%3A%20founder%20mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20accelerate%20this%20transition%2C%20I%20will%20personally%20go%20deeper%20into%20founder%20mode%2C%26quot%3B%20Kutylowski%20wrote%2C%20assembling%20%26quot%3Ba%20small%20taskforce%20that%20will%20further%20completely%20rethink%20how%20we%20build%20products%26quot%3B%20while%20putting%20%26quot%3BAI%20at%20the%20center%20of%20it%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKutylowski%20is%20leaning%20in%20deep%20into%20Silicon%20Valley%20culture.%20He's%20even%20opening%20a%20San%20Francisco%20office%2C%20he%20announced%20in%20the%20memo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22654fef2c-712b-4965-870b-37a3f98c5fc1%5C%22%3ELet's%20play%20layoff%20Mad%20Libs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20you%3B%20layoff%20memos%20are%20all%20starting%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-companies-layoff-announcements-sound-similar-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elook%20the%20same%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20like%20Block%2C%20Atlassian%2C%20and%20Snap%20have%20all%20referenced%20similar%20trends%20in%20their%20messages%20to%20staff.%20The%20companies%20need%20smaller%20teams%2C%20their%20executives%20say%2C%20and%20to%20work%20more%20effectively%20with%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELinear%20cofounder%20Tuomas%20Artman%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinear-cofounder-hiring-ai-driven-layoffs-joke-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epoked%20fun%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20format%20in%20a%20post%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20cost-cutting%20exercise%20or%20a%20reflection%20of%20anyone's%20performance%2C%26quot%3B%20Artman%20wrote%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fartman%2Fstatus%2F2052657017370661346%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E2052657017370661346%257Ctwgr%255E8efc5731b755424e40c3d308e279db01f1873668%257Ctwcon%255Es1_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.businessinsider.com%252Flinear-cofounder-hiring-ai-driven-layoffs-joke-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20X%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20simply%20reimagining%20every%20role%20for%20the%20agentic%20AI%20era.%20We're%20hiring.%20We're%20sorry%20about%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIs%20AI%20really%20the%20culprit%3F%20In%20February%2C%20Sam%20Altman%20said%20that%20some%20companies%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-ai-washing-layoffs-job-cuts-openai-india-summit-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BAI%20washing%26quot%3B%20their%20layoffs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20companies%20blamed%20AI%20for%20layoffs%20that%20would%20have%20happened%20otherwise%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20execs%20%E2%80%94%20like%20Kutylowski%20%E2%80%94%20say%20AI%20is%20radically%20changing%20how%20companies%20need%20to%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20does%20it%20take%20to%20operate%20as%20an%20enduring%20global%20AI%20company%20at%20this%20pace%20of%20change%2C%20and%20are%20we%20built%20for%20that%3F%26quot%3B%20Kutylowski%20asked%20in%20his%20memo.%20His%20team's%20honest%20answer%3A%20%26quot%3BNo.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-pilled-ceo-deepl-layoffs-memo-playbook-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778256295000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fdefd2e1443b8dc48e3340%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-pilled-ceo-deepl-layoffs-memo-playbook-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22DeepL%20laid%20off%20250%20employees.%20CEO%20Jarek%20Kutylowski's%20memo%20referenced%20AI%2C%20smaller%20teams%2C%20fewer%20layers%2C%20and%20founder%20mode.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hchandonnet%40insider.com%20(Henry%20Chandonnet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vodafone%20weighs%20stake%20transfer%20to%20shore%20up%20Voda%20Idea's%20capital%20base%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778254105000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F