0class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20empty%20classrooms%20to%20crowded%20mornings%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20day%20begins%20before%20dawn.%20By%208%20AM%2C%20Sangeeta%20is%20already%20at%20the%20school%20gate%2C%20greeting%20children%20who%20walk%20in%20barefoot%2C%20their%20satchels%20bouncing%20against%20their%20backs.%20The%20sight%20warms%20her%20now%2C%20but%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20always%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COut%20of%20130%20children%20enrolled%2C%20fewer%20than%2030%20attended%20regularly%20when%20I%20first%20joined%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20remembers%20her%20frustration.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20just%20sit%20inside%20the%20classroom%20and%20wait.%20So%20after%20school%20hours%2C%20I%20would%20go%20door%20to%20door%20in%20the%20afternoons.%20I%20sat%20with%20parents%2C%20explained%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F364214%2Fteachers-day-radhakrishnan-abdul-kalam-jyotirao-savitribai-phule-history-pics-gopal-krishna-gokhale%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhy%20education%20mattered%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20why%20it%20was%20worth%20sending%20their%20children%20to%20school%20instead%20of%20making%20them%20work.%20Many%20of%20these%20children%20did%20odd%20jobs%20and%20spent%20their%20earnings%20on%20tobacco%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CConvincing%20parents%20and%20children%20was%20a%20battle.%20I%20begged%20at%20times%2C%20I%20reasoned%20at%20others%2C%20and%20I%20kept%20asking%20them%20to%20send%20their%20children%20to%20school%20at%20least%20one%20more%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlowly%2C%20her%20persistence%20paid%20off.%20Within%20a%20month%2C%20attendance%20rose%20to%20100%20students.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20an%20easy%20victory%3B%20it%20meant%20knocking%20on%20doors%20daily%2C%20challenging%20traditions%20of%20child%20labour%2C%20and%20winning%20the%20trust%20of%20parents%20who%20had%20never%20experienced%20t