to%20give%20parents%20one%20piece%20of%20advice%2C%20it%20would%20be%20to%20stick%20to%20home-cooked%20meals.%20%3Cem%3EDal%3C%2Fem%3E-rice%20is%20great%2C%20but%20with%20gut%20health%20becoming%20such%20a%20challenge%2C%20we%20need%20to%20think%20beyond.%20What%20does%20our%20gut%20ask%20for%3F%20Fibre%20and%20variety.%20So%20yes%2C%20%3Cem%3Edal%3C%2Fem%3E-rice%20or%20%3Cem%3Edal-roti%3C%2Fem%3E%20daily%20is%20fine%2C%20but%20adding%20foods%20like%20moringa%20and%20millets%2C%20which%20are%20rich%20in%20antioxidants%2C%20can%20strengthen%20the%20gut%20and%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20our%20immune%20system.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandhya%20adds%3A%20%E2%80%9CKids%20today%20are%20smart.%20They%20know%20what%E2%80%99s%20healthy%2C%20but%20they%E2%80%99re%20more%20attracted%20to%20packaged%20foods.%20Our%20job%20as%20parents%20is%20to%20make%20the%20good%20stuff%20just%20as%20fun%2C%20creative%2C%20and%20irresistible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESave%20this%20cheat%20sheet%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInformation%20about%20what%20to%20eat%20and%20what%20to%20include%20in%20your%20kid%E2%80%99s%20diet%20can%20be%20a%20bit%20overwhelming.%20So%2C%20we%20have%20come%20up%20with%20the%20perfect%20cheat%20sheet%20for%20parents%20to%20look%20up%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThree%20easy%20millet%20swaps%20for%20lunchboxes%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EReplace%20white%20rice%20with%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20foxtail%20millet%20upma%20for%20a%20filling%20meal.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESwap%20maida-based%20wraps%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F412561%2Fmillets-summer-cooling-jowar-foxtail-ragi-temperature-diet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejowar%20or%20bajra%20%3Cem%3Erotis%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20stuffed%20with%20veggies.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETry%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Eladdoos%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20millet%20cookies%20as%20tiffin%20treats%20instead%20of%20packaged%20biscuits.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFive%20quickest%20microgreen%20uses%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESprinkle%20on%20%3Cem%3Edal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%20%3Cem%3Erotis%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20a%20nutrient%20boost.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMix%20into%20omelettes%20or%20scrambled%20eggs.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAdd%20as%20a%20topping%20for%20soups%20or%20noodles.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBlend%20a%20handful%20into%20smoothies%20or%20chutneys.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUse%20instead%20of%20coriander%20for%20a%20fresh%20garnish.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFour%20label-check%20rules%20for%20packaged%20foods%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELook%20at%20the%20first%203%20ingredients.%20If%20sugar%2C%20refined%20flour%2C%20or%20palm%20oil%20lead%20the%20list%2C%20skip%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EChoose%20products%20with%20less%20than%205%20g%20of%20sugar%20per%20serving.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPrefer%20snacks%20with%20whole%20grains%2C%20nuts%2C%20or%20seeds%20listed%20upfront.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAvoid%20items%20with%20too%20many%20unpronounceable%20additives%3B%20simple%20is%20better.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20handful%20of%20microgreens%20on%20a%20sandwich%20to%20a%20weekly%20batch%20of%20%3Cem%3Eragi%20laddoos%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20small%20steps%20can%20make%20a%20big%20difference.%20For%20India%2C%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20nutrition%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20reconnecting%20with%20roots%2C%20celebrating%20resilience%2C%20and%20giving%20our%20children%20the%20tools%20to%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757065097000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fmicrogreens_11zon-1756194438.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3